WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.946
HEY EVERYONE.

00:00:00.946 --> 00:00:03.067
WELCOME BACK TO MOVIE RECAP...

00:00:03.067 --> 00:00:06.007
TODAY I'M GOING TO SHOW YOU A MOVIE, TITLED

00:00:06.007 --> 00:00:07.002
PEPPERMINT.

00:00:07.002 --> 00:00:10.291
IT IS A 2018 AMERICAN VIGILANTE ACTION THRILLER FILM

00:00:10.291 --> 00:00:11.824
DIRECTED BY PIERRE MOREL

00:00:11.824 --> 00:00:13.515
AND STARRING JENNIFER GARNER... 

00:00:13.515 --> 00:00:16.125
THE MOVIE IS ABOUT A MOTHER WHO TRANSFORMS HERSELF

00:00:16.125 --> 00:00:18.231
INTO A VIGILANTE IN A QUEST FOR REVENGE

00:00:18.231 --> 00:00:21.267
AGAINST A DRUG CARTEL THAT KILLED HER DAUGHTER AND HER HUSBAND.

00:00:21.267 --> 00:00:22.969
LET'S START...

00:00:31.834 --> 00:00:36.029
THE FILM OPENS WITH WHAT APPEARS TO BE A STRUGGLE HAPPENING IN A CAR. 

00:00:36.029 --> 00:00:41.183
RILEY NORTH IS FIGHTING A GANGSTER WHO SLASHES HER LEG WITH HIS KNIFE.

00:00:41.183 --> 00:00:45.405
SHE GAINS THE UPPER HAND AND HOLDS A GUN UNDER HIS CHIN.

00:00:45.405 --> 00:00:48.109
RILEY ASKS IF HE REMEMBERS HER

00:00:48.109 --> 00:00:51.380
BUT HE SIMPLY RESPONDS WITH A DEFIANT, "F**K YOU!!!",

00:00:51.380 --> 00:00:54.366
BEFORE RILEY BLOWS HIS BRAINS OUT...

00:00:54.366 --> 00:00:58.613
RILEY GOES TO AN IMPOVERISHED NEIGHBORHOOD WHERE SHE HIDES OUT.

00:00:58.613 --> 00:01:03.747
SHE ENTERS HER VAN WHERE SHE TENDS TO HER LEG WOUND AND HAS A DRINK.

00:01:03.747 --> 00:01:05.513
SHE GOES THROUGH HER BELONGINGS

00:01:05.513 --> 00:01:08.958
AND OUTFALLS A BOX OF GIRL SCOUT COOKIES.

00:01:08.958 --> 00:01:10.578
FIVE YEARS EARLIER...

00:01:10.578 --> 00:01:13.205
RILEY IS SEEN WITH HER DAUGHTER CARLY,

00:01:13.205 --> 00:01:14.997
AFTER GETTING INTO AN ARGUMENT

00:01:14.997 --> 00:01:17.649
WITH ANOTHER GIRL SCOUT'S MOTHER, PEG,

00:01:17.649 --> 00:01:19.512
WHO COMPLAINS TO RILEY

00:01:19.512 --> 00:01:21.357
THAT THEY WERE SELLING ON THEIR TURF.

00:01:21.357 --> 00:01:25.752
LATER, RILEY AND CARLY STOPPED TO VISIT RILEY'S HUSBAND,

00:01:25.752 --> 00:01:27.811
CARLY'S FATHER CHRIS,

00:01:27.811 --> 00:01:29.578
WHO UNBEKNOWNST TO RILEY,

00:01:29.578 --> 00:01:33.837
IS ARRANGING SOME KIND OF SHADY DEAL WITH HIS CO-WORKER, MICKEY.

00:01:33.837 --> 00:01:36.422
RILEY THEN GOES TO WORK AT HER BANK

00:01:36.422 --> 00:01:42.240
AND IS TOLD TO WORK LATE, EVEN THOUGH IT'S CARLY'S BIRTHDAY.

00:01:42.479 --> 00:01:45.520
RILEY GOES HOME FOR CARLY'S BIRTHDAY PARTY,

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:48.673
ONLY TO FIND HER HUSBAND CHRIS AND HER DAUGHTER

00:01:48.673 --> 00:01:51.094
DISAPPOINTED BECAUSE NOBODY SHOWED UP,

00:01:51.094 --> 00:01:52.002
THANKS TO PEG,

00:01:52.002 --> 00:01:54.382
WHO SPITEFULLY THREW A HOLIDAY PARTY

00:01:54.382 --> 00:01:56.740
AND INVITED ALL THE OTHER KIDS

00:01:56.740 --> 00:02:00.423
BUT LEFT A VOICEMAIL JUST TO TAUNT RILEY AND CARLY.

00:02:00.423 --> 00:02:03.776
RILEY DECIDES NOT TO LET CARLY STAY SAD,

00:02:03.776 --> 00:02:07.289
SO SHE SUGGESTS THEY ALL GO TO THE CHRISTMAS CARNIVAL.

00:02:09.170 --> 00:02:12.439
AS THEY HEAD OUT, CHRIS CALLS MICKEY TO TELL HIM

00:02:12.439 --> 00:02:14.320
HE'S BACKING OUT OF THE DEAL...

00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:18.380
THE FAMILY LEAVES AND THEY ARE WATCHED BY A GANG-BANGER.

00:02:18.380 --> 00:02:22.622
HE CALLS HIS BOSS, CARTEL LEADER DIEGO GARCIA.

00:02:22.622 --> 00:02:25.635
GARCIA IS IN THE MIDDLE OF TORTURING MICKEY,

00:02:25.635 --> 00:02:27.810
WHO WAS APPARENTLY TRYING TO STEAL

00:02:27.810 --> 00:02:29.870
FROM GARCIA WITH CHRIS'S HELP...

00:02:29.870 --> 00:02:32.700
GARCIA ORDERS HIS GUY TO FOLLOW CHRIS

00:02:32.700 --> 00:02:35.736
RIGHT BEFORE HE DECAPITATES MICKEY.

00:02:36.634 --> 00:02:39.391
THE NORTHS ENJOY THEIR EVENING AT THE CARNIVAL

00:02:39.391 --> 00:02:41.694
AND END THE NIGHT WITH ICE CREAM.

00:02:41.694 --> 00:02:44.793
AS CHRIS AND CARLY WALK BACK TOWARD THE CAR,

00:02:44.793 --> 00:02:48.321
THREE GANG-BANGERS DRIVE UP BY THEM AND SHOOT THEM.

00:02:48.321 --> 00:02:50.447
RILEY GETS SHOT AS WELL

00:02:50.447 --> 00:02:52.487
BUT SHE MANAGES TO MAKE IT TO THE BODIES

00:02:52.487 --> 00:02:54.475
OF HER HUSBAND AND DAUGHTER...

00:02:54.475 --> 00:02:56.675
RILEY WAKES UP IN THE HOSPITAL

00:02:56.675 --> 00:02:59.780
AND MEETS WITH DETECTIVE STAN CARMICHAEL...

00:02:59.780 --> 00:03:01.198
HE TELLS RILEY,

00:03:01.198 --> 00:03:03.619
THAT THE SUSPECTS HAVE BEEN APPREHENDED

00:03:03.619 --> 00:03:05.874
AND HE GIVES RILEY THE PHOTO BOOTH

00:03:05.874 --> 00:03:08.418
PICTURES SHE TOOK WITH CHRIS AND CARLY.

00:03:09.773 --> 00:03:13.047
RILEY IS BROUGHT IN TO IDENTIFY THE GANG-BANGERS.

00:03:13.047 --> 00:03:15.598
SHE RECOGNIZES ALL THREE OF THEM

00:03:15.598 --> 00:03:17.669
BY THEIR FACE TATTOOS...

00:03:18.717 --> 00:03:22.294
LATER, AS SHE IS PACKING UP CHRIS AND CARLY'S THINGS,

00:03:22.294 --> 00:03:26.516
RILEY IS VISITED BY AN ATTORNEY NAMED, HENDERSON

00:03:26.516 --> 00:03:29.934
WHO ATTEMPTS TO BRIBE RILEY INTO DROPPING HER TESTIMONY

00:03:29.934 --> 00:03:32.881
AGAINST THE CRIMINALS THAT HE IS REPRESENTING...

00:03:32.881 --> 00:03:35.408
HE ALSO NOTICES SOME MEDICATION

00:03:35.408 --> 00:03:37.280
THAT RILEY IS TAKING BUT

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:39.625
SHE FORCES HIM OUT OF HER HOUSE...

00:03:41.917 --> 00:03:45.585
RILEY IS BROUGHT IN TO TESTIFY AGAINST THE GANG-BANGERS,

00:03:45.585 --> 00:03:48.520
BUT HENDERSON TRIES TO USE THE MEDICATION THING

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:51.353
AGAINST HER BY SAYING HER MEMORY WAS HAZY

00:03:51.353 --> 00:03:54.700
OR THAT SHE IS MENTALLY UNFIT TO REMEMBER THEM.

00:03:54.700 --> 00:03:58.292
JUDGE JAMES STEVENS RULES AGAINST RILEY'S FAVOR

00:03:58.292 --> 00:04:00.464
AND LETS THE KILLERS WALK...

00:04:00.464 --> 00:04:03.945
RILEY SNAPS AND TRIES TO ATTACK THE GANG-BANGERS

00:04:03.945 --> 00:04:06.108
BUT SHE IS TASED BY THE BAILIFF

00:04:06.108 --> 00:04:09.840
AND THE KILLERS LAUGH IN HER FACE.

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:13.037
RILEY IS BEING WHEELED AWAY TO A PSYCH WARD

00:04:13.037 --> 00:04:16.289
AND CARMICHAEL HOPS IN TO JOIN HER IN THE AMBULANCE

00:04:16.289 --> 00:04:20.401
BUT SHE GRABS AN OXYGEN TANK WHACKS CARMICHAEL ACROSS THE HEAD

00:04:20.401 --> 00:04:24.947
AND THEN RUNS OUT OF THE AMBULANCE, DISAPPEARING...

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:30.000
IN THE PRESENT DAY, CARMICHAEL MEETS WITH HIS PARTNER,

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:31.448
MOISES BELTRAN,

00:04:31.448 --> 00:04:34.016
AS THEY FIND THE BODIES OF THE THREE KILLERS

00:04:34.016 --> 00:04:37.759
HUNG UPSIDE DOWN FROM A FERRIS WHEEL...

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:41.160
RILEY GOES TO THE HOME OF JUDGE STEVENS

00:04:41.160 --> 00:04:43.532
AND TIES HIM UP AFTER BEATING HIM

00:04:43.532 --> 00:04:45.945
AND NAILING HIS HANDS TO THE TABLE.

00:04:45.945 --> 00:04:48.178
SHE MAKES SURE HE REMEMBERS HER

00:04:48.178 --> 00:04:52.540
AND SHE TELLS HIM THAT THE ROPE HE'S TIED UP WITH IS EXPLOSIVE.

00:04:52.540 --> 00:04:54.271
RILEY HOPS ON A BUS

00:04:54.271 --> 00:04:58.801
AND THEN DETONATESTHE ROPE, BLOWING STEVENS UP.

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:03.453
ON THE BUS, RILEY MEETS A YOUNG BOY

00:05:03.453 --> 00:05:07.420
AND SHE GIVES HIM A TOY THAT SHE SWIPED FROM STEVEN'S HOME.

00:05:07.420 --> 00:05:10.511
SHE NOTICES THE BOY'S FATHER IS DRUNK,

00:05:10.511 --> 00:05:12.187
AND AS THEY GET OFF THE BUS,

00:05:12.187 --> 00:05:16.712
THE MAN ENTERS A LIQUOR STORE WHILE HIS SON WAITS OUTSIDE.

00:05:16.712 --> 00:05:19.045
RILEY PISTOL WHIPS THE GUY

00:05:19.045 --> 00:05:21.844
AND ORDERS HIM TO NOT EVER DRINK AGAIN

00:05:21.844 --> 00:05:23.531
AND TO BE A GOOD FATHER

00:05:23.531 --> 00:05:24.993
OR SHE WILL FIND HIM

00:05:24.993 --> 00:05:26.846
SINCE SHE SAW HIS ID

00:05:26.846 --> 00:05:29.004
AND REMEMBERS HIS ADDRESS...

00:05:29.004 --> 00:05:33.411
SHE THEN FORCES THE CLERK TO GIVE HER HIS CAR BUT SHE AT LEAST,

00:05:33.411 --> 00:05:36.194
GIVES HIM MONEY FOR IT.

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:40.400
CARMICHAEL AND BELTRAN MEET WITH FELLOW DETECTIVE INMAN.

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:44.080
AS THEY SUSPECT RILEY TO BE BEHIND THESE KILLINGS,

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:46.312
SEEING AS HOW IT IS THE FIVE-YEAR

00:05:46.312 --> 00:05:48.833
ANNIVERSARY OF CHRIS AND CARLY'S MURDERS...

00:05:48.833 --> 00:05:52.130
AFTER THE TRIAL, RILEY ROBBED HER BANK

00:05:52.130 --> 00:05:55.352
AND STOLE MILITARY GRADE GUNS FROM A WAREHOUSE

00:05:55.352 --> 00:05:57.851
BEFORE GOING OFF THE GRID...

00:05:57.851 --> 00:05:59.829
CARMICHAEL THEN GETS A PHONE CALL

00:05:59.829 --> 00:06:01.865
TELLING HIM ABOUT STEVEN'S DEATH,

00:06:01.865 --> 00:06:06.996
AS WELL AS THE FACT THAT HENDERSON WAS FOUND FACE DOWN IN HIS POOL.

00:06:06.996 --> 00:06:11.459
THIS BASICALLY CONFIRMS FOR THEM THAT RILEY WAS INVOLVED...

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:16.349
RILEY DRIVES TO A PINATA STORE

00:06:16.349 --> 00:06:19.728
AND KILLS THE TWO MEN OUTSIDE BEFORE ENTERING...

00:06:21.399 --> 00:06:24.160
 A FIRE FIGHT ENSUES BUT RILEY KILLS ALL

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:27.308
THE MEN INSIDE EXCEPT FOR ONE, MARVIN...

00:06:27.308 --> 00:06:30.568
HE LATER REPORTS ON WHAT HAPPENED TO GARCIA

00:06:30.568 --> 00:06:34.382
AND MARVIN GETS KILLED FOR SPILLING HIS GUTS TO RILEY.

00:06:34.382 --> 00:06:36.505
IN ORDER TO GET RID OF RILEY,

00:06:36.505 --> 00:06:38.816
GARCIA ARRANGES FOR HIS MEN TO LURE

00:06:38.816 --> 00:06:40.751
HER TO A WAREHOUSE.

00:06:43.039 --> 00:06:44.903
SHE FINDS A BOMB THERE AND HIDES

00:06:44.903 --> 00:06:47.626
JUST AS GARCIA'S MEN DETONATE IT,

00:06:47.626 --> 00:06:50.568
OBLITERATING THE WHOLE BUILDING.

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:55.280
RILEY GETS OUT THROUGH THE SEWERS AND STEALS SOMEONE'S CAR

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:57.593
SO SHE CAN GO AFTER THE GUYS.

00:06:57.593 --> 00:07:01.003
SHE CATCHES UP, KILLS THEM, AND THEN MANAGES

00:07:01.003 --> 00:07:03.139
TO DRIVE TO GARCIA'S HOME...

00:07:03.139 --> 00:07:06.649
RILEY KILLS MOST OF THE MEN IN THERE

00:07:06.649 --> 00:07:09.199
BEFORE MAKING IT TO GARCIA HIMSELF.

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:11.392
SHE HAS HIS GUN TURNED ON HIM

00:07:11.392 --> 00:07:13.465
BUT BEFORE SHE CAN PULL THE TRIGGER,

00:07:13.465 --> 00:07:15.710
GARCIA'S DAUGHTER, WHO LOOKS ABOUT THE

00:07:15.710 --> 00:07:19.297
SAME AGE AS CARLY WHEN SHE DIED, WALKS IN.

00:07:19.297 --> 00:07:21.775
GARCIA STABS RILEY IN THE SIDE

00:07:21.775 --> 00:07:24.783
AND GETS OUT WITH HIS DAUGHTER AND HIS MEN.

00:07:25.391 --> 00:07:28.479
RILEY FLEES AND FINDS PEG'S HOME..

00:07:28.479 --> 00:07:30.451
SHE PUNCHES PEG IN THE FACE

00:07:30.451 --> 00:07:32.770
AND BARGES IN TO TEND TO HER WOUNDS

00:07:32.770 --> 00:07:34.953
RILEY HAS PEGGED TIED UP,

00:07:34.953 --> 00:07:36.934
POINTING OUT THAT PEG'S HUSBAND

00:07:36.934 --> 00:07:38.615
LEFT HER FOR ANOTHER WOMAN.

00:07:38.615 --> 00:07:40.471
RILEY THREATENS PEG

00:07:40.471 --> 00:07:42.384
AND EVEN MAKES HER PISS HERSELF

00:07:42.384 --> 00:07:45.840
BEFORE SHE LEAVES HER THERE...

00:07:46.879 --> 00:07:49.327
INMAN TRAVELS TO THE POOR NEIGHBORHOOD

00:07:49.327 --> 00:07:51.294
TO CONTINUE HER INVESTIGATION.

00:07:51.294 --> 00:07:53.499
SHE LEARNS FROM ONE OF THE MEN THERE

00:07:53.499 --> 00:07:55.442
THAT THE CRIME RATE IN THAT AREA

00:07:55.442 --> 00:07:58.952
WENT DOWN BECAUSE OF THE "ANGEL" LOOKING OUT FOR THEM.

00:07:58.952 --> 00:08:01.870
SHE IS THEN MET BY CARMICHAEL IN THAT AREA.

00:08:01.870 --> 00:08:04.233
WHEN SHE COMES CLOSE TO REALIZING

00:08:04.233 --> 00:08:07.868
SOMEBODY IN THE POLICE DEPARTMENT IS TIPPING OFF GARCIA,

00:08:07.868 --> 00:08:10.600
CARMICHAEL REVEALS HIMSELF TO BE DIRTY,

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:12.629
AND HE SHOOTS INMAN DEAD...

00:08:12.629 --> 00:08:15.541
GARCIA MEETS WITH CARMICHAEL IN THE AREA.

00:08:15.541 --> 00:08:17.722
RILEY FINDS INMAN'S BODY

00:08:17.722 --> 00:08:21.811
AND TAKES HER PHONE TO MAKE A LIVE VIDEO THAT HITS THE NEWS.

00:08:24.960 --> 00:08:27.155
AS GARCIA AND HIS MEN GATHER,

00:08:27.155 --> 00:08:30.129
RILEY EXPOSES CARMICHAEL AND GARCIA FOR

00:08:30.129 --> 00:08:31.795
THE SCUMBAGS THEY ARE,

00:08:31.795 --> 00:08:34.923
AND SHE INVITES THE POLICE AND THE NEWS TO THAT AREA.

00:08:34.923 --> 00:08:39.074
GARCIA THEN CALLS RILEY OUT USING A WALKIE-TALKIE

00:08:39.074 --> 00:08:40.564
AND ORDERS HER TO COME OUT

00:08:40.564 --> 00:08:43.863
OR HE WILL EXECUTE A LITTLE GIRL FROM THAT NEIGHBORHOOD.

00:08:43.863 --> 00:08:47.094
RILEY SURRENDERS AND APPROACHES GARCIA

00:08:47.094 --> 00:08:51.266
HE STARTS TO BEAT RILEY UP JUST BEFORE THE POLICE SHOW UP.

00:08:51.266 --> 00:08:53.549
THINKING CARMICHAEL SET HIM UP,

00:08:53.549 --> 00:08:55.350
GARCIA SHOOTS HIM DEAD.

00:08:55.350 --> 00:08:58.825
GARCIA'S MEN ARE ARRESTED AS HE TRIES TO FLEE,

00:08:58.825 --> 00:09:00.989
BUT RILEY CATCHES UP TO HIM...

00:09:00.989 --> 00:09:02.864
SHE HOLDS HER GUN AT HIM,

00:09:02.864 --> 00:09:05.616
AND THE POLICE HAVE THEIR WEAPONS DRAWN ON HER.

00:09:05.616 --> 00:09:08.965
BELTRAN BEGS RILEY NOT TO SHOOT GARCIA,

00:09:08.965 --> 00:09:10.592
AND HE TAUNTS HER SAYING

00:09:10.592 --> 00:09:12.977
THAT SHE'LL BE IN PRISON LONGER THAN HIM...

00:09:12.977 --> 00:09:16.167
RILEY SAYS "WE'RE NOT GOING TO PRISON",

00:09:16.167 --> 00:09:17.777
AND SHE SHOOTS HIM IN THE HEAD,

00:09:17.777 --> 00:09:20.257
AND THE POLICE RETURN FIRE...

00:09:20.257 --> 00:09:22.114
RILEY MANAGES TO FLEE

00:09:22.114 --> 00:09:25.252
BUT BELTRAN SAYS HE KNOWS WHERE SHE'S GOING.

00:09:26.316 --> 00:09:30.750
THE COPS FIND RILEY AT THE CEMETERY AT CHRIS AND CARLY'S GRAVE.

00:09:30.750 --> 00:09:34.565
SHE BREAKS DOWN WEEPING AS BELTRAN APPROACHES HER...

00:09:34.565 --> 00:09:37.299
RILEY FEELS SHE IS READY TO DIE THERE,

00:09:37.299 --> 00:09:39.517
BUT BELTRAN SAYS OTHERWISE.

00:09:40.805 --> 00:09:42.716
ON THE LAST SCENE OF THIS FILM,

00:09:42.716 --> 00:09:44.311
RILEY IS IN THE HOSPITAL,

00:09:44.311 --> 00:09:46.784
AND THE NEWS REPORTS ON HOW CIVILIANS

00:09:46.784 --> 00:09:49.910
SEE RILEY AS SOME KIND OF HEROIC VIGILANTE,

00:09:49.910 --> 00:09:53.098
BUT THE POLICE SAY SHE WILL ANSWER FOR HER CRIMES.

00:09:53.098 --> 00:09:57.325
BELTRAN WALKS INTO RILEY'S ROOM AND SLIPS A KEY INTO HER HAND,

00:09:57.325 --> 00:10:01.836
LETTING HER REMOVE HER HANDCUFFS AND ESCAPE ONCE AGAIN.

